its the best truck game ive ever played its not like those truck mobile games this is somthing differnt 

for your mom if its not buyng you the game:
hey listen buy this game to your son ill develop his skills of driving and his barin so be a little good its not like it costs 1000000 dollars

If only I already play this game when I was still kid, I'll proudly answer that I want to be a truck driver when the teacher asks. I never expected that this kind of game will give me soothing and relaxing experience. Perfect to be played on weekdays after work.

Some request/suggestion for the Devs:
(1) Please make the ability to toggle on/off the legend (icons) on World Map. Sometimes it really hard to see unexplored parts that were covered by map icons;
(2) Possibility to get the trucks dirty would be nice;
(3) Visual damage on your truck after crash or collision would be nice.
